<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>Order Confirmation Email</title>
</head>

<body style="background:#e9f2fb;padding:0;">

<table width="90%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" align="center" style="max-width:900px;">
	<thead>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#e9f2fb" style="height:10px;font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="middle" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="padding-bottom:5px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:10px;">
				<img src="http://www.greenmoney.com.au/images/logo-voucher.png" width="160" height="29" alt="GreenMoney" />
			</td>
		</tr>
	</thead>
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#e9f2fb" style="height:10px;font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="height:10px;font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="color:#000;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:14px;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:12px;padding-right:12px;padding-top:0;line-height:20px;">
				<p style="margin-top:0;">Hi @Model.FirstName</p>

				<p>Congratulations! You have redeemed the following rewards on @Model.Time.ToString("dd-MM-yyyy"):</p>
				
				<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
					<thead>
						<tr>
							<th style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-top:7px;">Reward</th>
							<th style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-left:7px;padding-top:7px;padding-right:7px;">Points</th>
							<th style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-left:7px;padding-top:7px;padding-right:7px;">Pay</th>
							<th style="text-align:right; padding-bottom:7px;padding-top:7px;white-space:nowrap;">Your voucher</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						@foreach (var item in Model.Items) {
							<tr>
								<td style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-top:7px;">@item.Name</td>
								<td style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-left:7px;padding-top:7px;padding-right:7px;">@item.Points.ToString("#,##0")</td>
								<td style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-left:7px;padding-top:7px;padding-right:7px;">@item.DollarCost.ToString("$#,##0.00")</td>
                                @if (item.DollarCost == 0)
                                {
								    <td style="text-align:right; padding-bottom:7px;padding-top:7px;white-space:nowrap;"><a href="@(Model.VoucherUrl)/@(item.VoucherId)" style="color:#5da9dd;text-decoration:underline;"><b>View voucher</b></a></td>
                                }
                                else
                                {
                                    <td></td>
                                }
                                    
							</tr>
						}
						<tr>
							<th style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-top:7px;">Total</th>
							<td style="text-align:left; padding-bottom:7px;padding-left:7px;padding-top:7px;padding-right:7px;"><b>@Model.Total.ToString("#,##0")</b></td>
							<td colspan="2"></td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
				
                <b>Once the above payment has been received, your product will be shipped to your nominated address.</b>

                @if (Model.HasVouchers)
                {
				    <p>Click <b>View voucher</b> to view the instructions on how to redeem each reward.</p>
                }
				
				<p>Please remember to read all the terms and conditions set out in the voucher and on the GreenMoney website.</p>
				
				<p>
					Regards<br>
					Suzanna &amp; the GreenMoney team<br>
					<a href="http://www.greenmoney.com.au" style="color:#5da9dd;text-decoration:underline;">www.greenmoney.com.au</a>
				</p>
				
				<p style="color:#666666;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:0;">
					<br>
					<a href="http://www.greenmoney.com.au/privacy-policy" style="color:#5da9dd;text-decoration:underline;">Privacy policy</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://www.greenmoney.com.au/learn-more/faq" style="color:#5da9dd;text-decoration:underline;">FAQ</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href="http://www.greenmoney.com.au/learn-more/contact-us" style="color:#5da9dd;text-decoration:underline;">Contact us</a>
				</p>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#ffffff" style="height:10px;font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#e9f2fb" style="height:10px;font-size:1px;">&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

</body>

</html>